{"tid":537771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界有無最愛","createTime":"2018-01-23T04:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T19:36:12.000Z","uid":89494,"like":31,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60fba2e832cce61ff600a1659c82a0fa33ec863f","tid":537771,"uid":89494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"一個最愛既人<br />\n可能唔可以同你行完成個人生<br />\n唔可以一齊<br />\n但呢個人就算你有另一段感情<br />\n你都知道雖然已經冇可能但佢仍然會住係你個心入面<br />\n默默咁存在<br />\n<br />\n定係<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個世界根本無最愛<br />\n可能你依家會覺得呢個係最愛<br />\n但當呢個完結左<br />\n下一個黎既時候<br />\n最愛已被改寫？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有最愛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇最愛"},{"pid":"41b8921939a38514c339e7b784f4836ff4c10283","tid":537771,"uid":20379,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e309341f08d24932c64e3223225ac3de577d4595","tid":537771,"uid":45148,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"呢個世界講timing<br />\n你timing好既 咩都可以得到<br />\ntiming差既 只可以珍惜擁有的"},{"pid":"8c89b0640e1183331119780e9c0ae2fb5d8d40b5","tid":537771,"uid":89494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b8921939a38514c339e7b784f4836ff4c10283","tid":537771,"uid":20379,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"姐係點"},{"pid":"5b98dccd1f39e5f41747e5cbc08d538a0da9da44","tid":537771,"uid":74262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e609f3d15d4221b3b672d74be6205daedd0dce0","tid":537771,"uid":89494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b98dccd1f39e5f41747e5cbc08d538a0da9da44","tid":537771,"uid":74262,"like":6,"dislike":0